📧 Newsletter & Email Campaign Manager API
------------------------------------------------

A secure backend API for managing mailing lists, creating email campaigns, and scheduling email delivery. This project simulates email sending using logs instead of real email integrations.

🚀 Features
-----------------
🔐 User Authentication & Authorization (JWT-based)
📬 Mailing List Management
📝 Create, update, and manage email campaigns
🔗 Link campaigns to mailing lists
⏰ Schedule email campaigns (simulated)
📊 Campaign status tracking (e.g., DRAFT, SENT)
🔍 Pagination and filtering for campaigns

🧩 Functional Requirements
-----------------------------
1. Authentication

User registration & login
Secure authentication using JWT
Password encryption using BCrypt

2. Mailing List Management

Create mailing lists
Add/remove subscribers
Manage subscriber details

3. Campaign Management

Users can:

Create and edit campaigns
Link campaigns to mailing lists
Define subject, content, and schedule
Update campaign status (e.g., SENT)

4. Email Sending (Simulation)

Campaigns are "sent" using logs
No real email service required
Helps test scheduling & workflow
5. Query Features
View all campaigns with pagination
Filter campaigns by status

